s2","ord":1,"text":"Her classmates cheered, and Ms. Park said, \"Let's make every week Eco Week.\"","translation_ko":"친구들이 환호했고, 박 선생님이 말했어요. \"매주를 에코 주간으로 만들어 봐요.\"","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-138-the-eco-challenge/audio/p12-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Her","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"classmates","charStart":4,"charEnd":14,"startMs":240,"endMs":720},{"word":"cheered","charStart":15,"charEnd":22,"startMs":720,"endMs":1240},{"word":"and","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1820,"endMs":1900},{"word":"Ms","charStart":28,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2080},{"word":"Park","charStart":32,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2260,"endMs":2340},{"word":"said","charStart":37,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2340,"endMs":2640},{"word":"Let's","charStart":44,"charEnd":49,"startMs":3200,"endMs":3460},{"word":"make","charStart":50,"charEnd":54,"startMs":3460,"endMs":3620},{"word":"every","charStart":55,"charEnd":60,"startMs":3620,"endMs":3980},{"word":"week","charStart":61,"charEnd":65,"startMs":3980,"endMs":4380},{"word":"Eco","charStart":66,"charEnd":69,"startMs":4380,"endMs":4800},{"word":"Week","charStart":70,"charEnd":74,"startMs":4800,"endMs":5000}]},{"id":"daily-138-the-eco-challenge-p12-s3","ord":2,"text":"Jun smiled and thought, \"We started small, but now we are a team.\"","translation_ko":"준은 미소 지으며 생각했어요. '작게 시작했지만, 이제 우리는 한 팀이야.'","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-138-the-eco-challenge/audio/p12-s3.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Jun","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":440},{"word":"smiled","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":440,"endMs":1000},{"word":"and","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1340},{"word":"thought","charStart":15,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1560},{"word":"We","charStart":25,"charEnd":27,"startMs":2020,"endMs":2320},{"word":"started","charStart":28,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2320,"endMs":2640},{"word":"small","charStart":36,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2640,"endMs":3140},{"word":"but","charStart":43,"charEnd":46,"startM